Hi, your rules looks like ok. You can try search for these registry key to see if they exists :<br />
<pre><code>&lt;sdp:IsInstallable&gt; 
   &lt;lar:And&gt; 
      &lt;bar:RegSzToVersion RegType32=&quot;true&quot; Data=&quot;18.0.0.209&quot; Comparison=&quot;LessThan&quot; Value=&quot;Version&quot; Subkey=&quot;Software\Macromedia\FlashPlayerPlugin&quot; Key=&quot;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE&quot;/&gt;
      &lt;bar:RegKeyExists RegType32=&quot;true&quot; Subkey=&quot;Software\Macromedia\FlashPlayerPlugin&quot; Key=&quot;HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE&quot;/&gt;
   &lt;/lar:And&gt; 
&lt;/sdp:IsInstallable&gt;</code></pre>

Also, you can edit the update and look at the metadata of the MSI file. There is some &quot;IsInstallable&quot; rules in it.<br />
